<p>I wish you the best of luck in obtaining medical records.  I painstakingly went through this same process last fall and was told by the hospital they do not store medical records beyond 10 years. If the individual state can be sued, all power to us.  Not certain any of us will locate an attorney who will be willing to take on our cases.  Each attorney I spoke to last fall said no, they would not take their time for such a case because of the time lapse and the odds of winning. Willing to join in to try again.</p>
