				<p>I could not possibly agree more. There needs to be a national law forbidding child abuse of any sort; especially sexual. There are several states who are trying to add child sexual abuse to their capital charges list. I say I support it 100%. Though it should be federal law, we can only hope that with their petitions comes awareness and the desire to follow. There is no other way to stop the continual pain and suffering of infants and children through adolescence upward.</p>
